<div class="background-overlay">
  <h1 class="about-header">About Me</h1>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4 profile-img">
      <%= image_tag "profile.png", width: 250, alt: "profile image", class: "about-img" %>
      <div class="skills about-toggle-btns">
        <p>
          <button class="btn about-btn btn-block" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#skills" aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="skills">
            Skills
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="skills">
            <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %> </h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-dark" role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <p class="about-paragraphs">
        Hey there, thank you for stopping by. Incase you didn’t
        catch it, my name is Brian, I live in Arizona, and I build beautiful websites, front to back.
        I’m a passionate Ruby on Rails developer with over a year of programming experience. I have several awesome projects
        that can be accessed on my <%= link_to  "portfolio", portfolios_path, class: "about-links" %> page. Along with Ruby on Rails, I love Javascript and like to play around with React, and NodeJS. For more info you can get ahold
        of me via the <%= link_to  "contact", contact_path, class: "about-links" %> page.
      </p>
      <p class="about-paragraphs">
        Along with being a
        coding wizard who turns patience into software, I’m a father and husband, I’m a life long guitarist, and I
        like being a nice guy too. I also, love reading, coffee, yoga, food, meditation, video games, and learning any and all things.
      </p>
      <div class="about-toggle-btns">
        <p>
          <button class="btn about-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#jobHistory" aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="jobHistory">
            Job History
          </button>
          <button class="btn about-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#education" aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="education">
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              WordPress Developer, Webpartnerr.com, October 2018 to present.
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Technician, Global Data Services, October 2016 to May 2018
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Administrative Assistant, That Paralegal Place, November 2012 to September 2016
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Tech Talent South Immersive Coding Bootcamp, Studied Ruby on Rails, Javascript and the fundamentals of programming and web design.
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              South West Institute of Healing Arts, Studied Life Coaching and Holistic Nutrition.
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Glendale Community College, Studied mathematics, philosophy and psychology.
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>